  <summary date="2021-02-18T17:27:31Z" status="Introduced in House">Teachers Are Leaders Act of 2019

This bill reauthorizes through FY2025 and revises the Teacher Quality Partnership Grant Program, including by replacing a school leadership grant program with a teacher leader development program. The new program awards grants for the professional development of teachers who remain in the classroom while also carrying out&#160;formalized leadership responsibilities.</summary>
